title: Looking for Jungler
body:
Hello all im looking for anyone who would be interested in playing Jungle for a squad of five this Monday 4th Feb, Myself and a few guys are planning on having a full day of league to practice but our jungler has othe commitments so thought I would check on here to see if any is interested. the team is practically full of low gold elo player so don't feel to shy aha. add me in game xheroborn

TLDR: Looking for jungler for Monday the 4th as team is planning on practicing thanks 


p.s all aged between 20-23 <3all though sometimes I double think this :D
